    "content": "I wanted to submit my own tab for this because I didn't like the other ones.\r\n\r\nHere is the instrumental version that I used for the time stamps \r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f69sSPoX2tQ\r\n\r\n[Intro](0:05-0:36)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-5~---------------|-7~---------------|\r\nD|-5~---------------|-7~---------------|\r\nA|-3~---------------|-5~---------------|\r\nE|------------------|------------------|     x2[/tab]\r\n\r\n[Verse] (0:36-1:16)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------4-----------|------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------2-----5-7---5--2-4-5/7|---------------2-----5----4----2-2--------|\r\nA|--0----2-0-2/4---0-0-----------------|--0----2-0-2/4---0-0-----------------5----|\r\nE|-------------------------------------|------------------------------------------|     x3\r\n  ........\"I wanted to be\"......................\"And talk about\"..................[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------4-----------|------------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------2-----5-7---5--2-4-5/7|---------------2-----5----4----2-2--------|\r\nA|--0----2-0-2/4---0-0-----------------|--0----2-0-2/4---0-0-----------------5~---|\r\nE|-------------------------------------|------------------------------------------|     x1 Hold the final note[/tab]\r\n\r\n[Chorus] (1:16-1:46)\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------|-------------------------------|\r\nD|------5-4---------------------2|------5-4----------------------|\r\nA|----------5-2-------------2-5--|----------5-2------------------|\r\nE|3~--x----------0~---2-3-5------|3~--x----------0~--x--0-0------|     x1\r\n \"Something happens\".............\"Find out\"......[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|-------------------------------|-------------------------------|\r\nD|------5-4---------------------2|-------------------------------|\r\nA|----------5-2-------------2-5--|5~-----------------------------|\r\nE|3~--x----------0~---2-3-5------|-------------------------------|     x1\r\n